    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Affordable project car with good upside for the right buyer. This one is in poor overall condition and will need significant cosmetic and mechanical work, so it\u2019s best suited for a handy owner, restorer, or parts/project use. If you\u2019re looking for a fixer-upper and know what you\u2019re getting into, this could be a worthwhile opportunity at a realistic price.",
