    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, well-kept vehicle in truly mint condition. Inside and out, it presents beautifully with a like-new appearance, excellent paint, a very clean interior, and no meaningful signs of wear worth noting. It runs and drives exactly as it should, feels tight and well sorted on the road, and has clearly been cared for properly. If you\u2019ve been looking for an outstanding example that needs nothing and is ready to enjoy immediately, this is the kind of car to see.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Fair-condition vehicle that is still usable and presentable, but it shows clear signs of age and regular use. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear inside and out, including blemishes in the paint, interior wear, and other imperfections consistent with a vehicle that has not been restored or heavily reconditioned. It should suit a buyer looking for practical transportation at a more affordable price, as long as they are comfortable with a car that is not cosmetically clean or close to showroom condition.",
      "price": 19800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer seeking dependable basic transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for someone who values function and value over perfection, but it still offers a solid opportunity to get on the road without a major investment. A smart pick for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone looking for inexpensive wheels.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right owner? This one isn\u2019t winning any beauty contests, but it starts, moves, and offers a solid low-cost option for someone who needs basic transport, a first project, or a handy spare vehicle. A sensible buy for the practical shopper who sees value where others might pass it by.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest driver with solid bones and plenty of life left. Starts up, runs, and offers the kind of straightforward mechanical feel that makes it a great budget commuter, first car, or hands-on project. The powertrain feels willing, the chassis is composed, and it\u2019s the sort of car that rewards someone who appreciates simple, dependable transportation. Not a showpiece, but a practical, usable vehicle with real value for the money. Priced to move for someone who wants affordable wheels without unnecessary drama.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car right now. Honest used vehicle with wear, but priced to move fast. Great for a fixer, work commuter, or backup ride.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with a story still unfolding\u2014full of character, presence, and the kind of old-school grit that makes a great project, budget runabout, or creative build. It\u2019s not pretending to be perfect, and that\u2019s part of the appeal: honest, approachable, and ready for someone with vision to make it their own. Whether you need affordable wheels, a weekend tinkering companion, or a platform with personality, this one offers a lot of opportunity for the price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
